MooseX-Exception-Base

This module provides basic helpers to make Moose exception objects, is
somewhat similar to L<Exception::Class> in usage.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc MooseX::Exception::Base

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=MooseX-Exception-Base

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/MooseX-Exception-Base

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/MooseX-Exception-Base

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/MooseX-Exception-Base/

    Source Code
        git://github.com/ivanwills/MooseX-Exception-Base.git

